                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 今⽇公佈了 2024 年 App Store Awards 得獎名單，表揚協助用户應對更多工作、發揮更多創意，以至與親朋戚友更緊密聯繫的 app 及遊戲。今年 App Store Awards 新增全新 Apple Vision Pro 類別，突顯空間計算世界的驚人成就。App Store Award 得獎作品由 45 份入圍作品中挑選 17 個應用程式，肯定世界各地開發者為用户帶來的卓越體驗、設計與創新。</p><div class="pagebody text component"><div class="component-content"><h2 class="pagebody-header"><strong>Apps</strong></h2><p><strong>「年度 iPhone App」</strong></p><p><b>App：</b>《<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/kino-pro-video-camera/id6472380172">Kino</a>》</p><p><b>開發者：</b>Lux Optics Inc.</p><p>《Kino》將日常生活瞬間變成電影傑作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121153126-694x525.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="525" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121153126-694x525.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121153126.jpg 1190w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121153002-688x580.jpg" alt="" width="688" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121153002-688x580.jpg 688w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121153002.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 688px" /></p><p><strong>「年度 iPad App」</strong></p><p><b>App：《</b><a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/moises-the-musicians-app/id1515796612">Moises</a><b>》</b></p><p><b>開發者：</b>Moises Systems Inc.</p><p>《Moises》以 AI 工具提升音樂練習體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121144203-694x519.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121144203-694x519.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2