re.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2-694x439.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2-694x439.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2.jpg 1090w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">步驟 3：此時根據介面指示完成操作即可。其中你需要關閉 iPhone 的「尋找」功能，然後安裝 WhatsApp。軟件也會自動在你的 Android 裝置上安裝自定的 WhatsApp 以讀取資料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/3-694x439.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/3-694x439.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/3.jpg 1090w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">步驟 4：WhatsApp iOS to Android 的時間取決於檔案的大小，所以你只需要耐心等待過程完成即可，就那麼簡單！</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">你還可以查看以下影片教學進行轉移：</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_42296"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CwyyZjlvvew?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2></h2><br /><b>
